{"tid":178670,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下唔夠一年就被公司裁員有冇得賠?","createTime":"2017-03-29T16:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T06:10:36.000Z","uid":43843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c0ab20888e17a4464ab8c676aade7395ff0e65","tid":178670,"uid":43843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"唉，返左份工唔夠一年就被通知黎緊成為裁員既一分子，想問下有冇巴絲知會唔會有賠償？<br />\n<br />\n我上網睇勞工署話做夠24個月先有遣散費賠.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4e1c24c5b01d38745f253a8d46dc0cdf808d37","tid":178670,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"你都睇左 問黎做乜？"},{"pid":"658c7514cf29df5a41b8633249d6cc889e688c20","tid":178670,"uid":65905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"唔係公司執笠先拎遣散費？比人炒應該係補一個月糧？"},{"pid":"f83f4446c892efdd1716c144983c7f2475eb802b","tid":178670,"uid":43843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都睇左 問黎做乜？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老細同我講左，話HR遲下會揾我，所以未知有冇得賠。我未試過... 所以先問下有冇巴絲知係點賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575267ca804e79a8e9e4968dbc1237d6e8723fc3","tid":178670,"uid":43843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係公司執笠先拎遣散費？比人炒應該係補一個月糧？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係好知呀，我上網search大部份巴絲討論既都係做左幾年，冇乜人講話唔夠1年被人裁係點.... 都係想參考下... <br />\n<br />\n如果即走都係賠得一個月，唉，而家揾工咁難，真係隨時揾幾個月，個一個月糧點頂到.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6e442c536ed32e7bd1131ebb31b8814a8beb7b","tid":178670,"uid":43621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"冇得陪<br />\n邊行？"},{"pid":"51fc31435c9c35bd1bf5bd5f11e5192c27adcd55","tid":178670,"uid":11285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"一個月代通知實有嘅"},{"pid":"849746f2f97d1b10d1b1cab5fe47f913acc5188e","tid":178670,"uid":43843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個月代通知實有嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個時期揾工閒閒地可以揾幾個月至半年<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611b5e27308cf91360315a17c3405b4694301e8a","tid":178670,"uid":43843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇得陪<br />\n邊行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點賠，如無意外應該得一個月<br />\n<br />\n廣告業..."},{"pid":"a4ec884b497bda0bc00550653b171ce0bfb89f0f","tid":178670,"uid":65905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個月代通知實有嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個時期揾工閒閒地可以揾幾個月至半年<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家開始搵啦 老細講得比你知算好的了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31364ce6852866a015d28dfce50eabb90a39fae5","tid":178670,"uid":29703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇得陪<br />\n邊行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點賠，如無意外應該得一個月<br />\n<br />\n廣告業...</blockquote><br />\n叫你坐月 賠都唔使賠 ，按例而言即炒最多賠一個月通知金俾你 另外點解你有無睇清楚你份合約點寫？"},{"pid":"96c89ca4c1ded3640c7bc5622044c9cccbb0fd67","tid":178670,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"賠代通知金"}]}